      "content": "ugh just landed in dubai after like 14 hours on a plane and my chest feels all sharp and weird whenever i try to take a deep breath. i'm also kinda short of breath. honestly i'm probably just super stressed from the travel and the jetlag... u think its just a panic attack or something?",
